description.en:
Netkoin Liquid is a utility token designed to enhance and optimise the functionality of the NTK token and Netkoin ecosystem. 

A two-token (dual token) system is made possible by introducing a secondary utility token; Netkoin Liquid. This token will compliment the NTK token, enhancing and optimising the functionality of the Netkoin ecosystem.
